Top-performing models are those with the highest average performance metric values; 
performance metrics (e.g., accuracy, precision) used to evaluate the models can vary;
the average market capitalization is used to assess the size of the companies; 
access counts indicate the number of times the datasets have been accessed.

sql:
SELECT dataset_id, MAX(volume) AS max_volume, MIN(volume) AS min_volume
FROM volumes
GROUP BY dataset_id;

SELECT symbol_name, created_at
FROM symbols
ORDER BY created_at DESC;

SELECT exchange_name, url
FROM exchanges
ORDER BY exchange_name ASC;
